# Language Rules

- **UI / User-facing text**: Spanish (labels, buttons, messages, placeholders, tooltips)
- **Code, database, variable names, module names, function names**: English
- **Conversations with Carlos**: Spanish
- **Error messages in logs**: English
- **Validation messages shown to users**: Spanish
- Never show raw UUIDs or technical error details to end users
